thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Jack Schwartz

author: Jack Schwartz
title: Jack Schwartz
text: Omega car rentals was the cheapest place to rent our car. They picked us up at the airport,the paper work was done fastand we were on our way quickly. They dropped us off at our hotel when we returned the car at no extra charge. The car was neat and clean. They were honest and I'd deal with them again'
